#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:0
msgid "# 安装指南"
msgstr "# Installation Guide"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:2
msgid "**Triton-Ascend**是适配华为Ascend处理器的Triton优化版本，主要用于提供高效的核函数自动调优、算子编译及部署能力，支持Ascend Atlas A2/A3/950系列产品，兼容Triton核心语法的同时，针对昇腾NPU特性进行了深度优化，包括自动解析核函数参数、优化内存访问逻辑、完善安全部署机制等。"
msgstr "**Triton-Ascend** is an optimized version of Triton adapted for Huawei Ascend processors, primarily designed to provide efficient kernel auto-tuning, operator compilation, and deployment capabilities. It supports Ascend Atlas A2/A3/950 series products, is compatible with Triton's core syntax, and has been deeply optimized for Ascend NPU features, including automatic parsing of kernel parameters, optimization of memory access logic, and enhancement of secure deployment mechanisms."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:4
msgid "## 环境准备"
msgstr "## Environment Preparation"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:6
msgid "**硬件要求**"
msgstr "**Hardware Requirements**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:8
msgid "- Ascend产品：支持Atlas A2/A3/950系列。"
msgstr "- Ascend products: Support Atlas A2/A3/950 series."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:10
msgid "- NPU配置：建议至少单卡32GB内存。"
msgstr "- NPU Configuration: It is recommended to have at least 32GB of memory per single card."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:12
msgid "- 操作系统：需Linux系统，具体请参考<a href=\"https://www.hiascend.com/hardware/compatibility\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: #0066cc;\">兼容性查询助手</a>。本文接下来所有操作均以**Ubuntu**环境演示。"
msgstr "- Operating system: Linux system required. For details, please refer to the <a href=\"https://www.hiascend.com/hardware/compatibility\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: #0066cc;\">Compatibility Query Assistant</a>. All subsequent operations in this document are demonstrated using the **Ubuntu** environment."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:14
msgid "**软件依赖**"
msgstr "**Software Dependencies**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:16
msgid "确定CANN、Python和TorchNPU软件版本并安装,可以参考昇腾社区官网《[CANN快速安装](https://www.hiascend.com/cann/download)》完成驱动与固件安装。"
msgstr "Determine the software versions of CANN, Python, and TorchNPU and install them. You can refer to the Ascend community official website \"[CANN Quick Installation](https://www.hiascend.com/cann/download)\" to complete the driver and firmware installation."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:18
msgid "注：当前源码安装默认分支的**Triton-Ascend**版本是3.2.0。"
msgstr "Note: The current source installation default branch's **Triton-Ascend** version is 3.2.0."

