#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:22
msgid "## 快速安装"
msgstr "## Quick Installation"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:24
msgid ""
"```bash\n"
"# 以安装 triton-ascend 3.2.1 为例\n"
"pip install triton-ascend==3.2.1 --extra-index-url=https://triton-ascend.osinfra.cn/pypi/simple\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:26
msgid "## 源码安装"
msgstr "## Source Code Installation"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:28
msgid "### 安装依赖"
msgstr "### Install Dependencies"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:30
msgid ""
"```bash\n"
"apt update\n"
"apt install zlib1g-dev clang-15 lld-15\n"
"apt install ccache # optional\n"
"update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/clang clang /usr/bin/clang-15 100\n"
"update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/clang++ clang++ /usr/bin/clang++-15 100\n"
"pip install ninja cmake wheel pybind11 # build-time dependencies\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:32
msgid "### 编译Triton-Ascend"
msgstr "### Compiling Triton-Ascend"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:34
msgid ""
"```bash\n"
"git clone https://github.com/triton-lang/triton-ascend.git && cd triton-ascend\n"
"git checkout main\n"
"pip install -e .\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:36
msgid "### 自定义LLVM构建（可选）"
msgstr "### Custom LLVM Build (Optional)"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:38
msgid "如果需要自定义构建LLVM过程的，可以执行下面的步骤去编译Triton-Ascend。"
msgstr "If you need to customize the LLVM build process, you can follow the steps below to compile Triton-Ascend."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:40
msgid "1. **代码准备**：通过`git checkout`检出指定版本的LLVM源码并应用补丁。"
msgstr "1. **Code Preparation**: Check out the specified version of the LLVM source code using `git checkout` and apply the patches."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:42
msgid ""
"    ```bash\n"
"    git clone --no-checkout https://github.com/llvm/llvm-project.git\n"
"    cd llvm-project\n"
"    git checkout f6ded0be897e2878612dd903f7e8bb85448269e5\n"
"    wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/triton-lang/triton-ascend/refs/heads/main/third_party/ascend/patch/llvm_patch_f6ded0b.patch\n"
"    git apply llvm_patch_f6ded0b.patch\n"
"    ```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:44
msgid "2. **构建LLVM**：路径`{PATH_TO}`为用户第一步检出LLVM源码的路径。"
msgstr "2. **Building LLVM**: The path `{PATH_TO}` is the path where the user checked out the LLVM source code in the first step."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:46
msgid ""
"    ```bash\n"
"    # /path/to/llvm-install 路径为用户规划的llvm安装路径,需根据实际调整\n"
"    export LLVM_INSTALL_PREFIX=/path/to/llvm-install\n"
"    cd {PATH_TO}/llvm-project\n"
"    mkdir build\n"
"    cd build\n"
"    cmake ../llvm \\\n"
"        -G Ninja \\\n"
"        -DCMAKE_C_COMPILER=/usr/bin/clang-15 \\\n"
"        -DCMAKE_CXX_COMPILER=/usr/bin/clang++-15 \\\n"
"        -DCMAKE_LINKER=/usr/bin/lld-15 \\\n"
"        -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release \\\n"
"        -DLLVM_ENABLE_ASSERTIONS=ON \\\n"
"        -DLLVM_ENABLE_PROJECTS=\"mlir;llvm;lld\" \\\n"
"        -DLLVM_TARGETS_TO_BUILD=\"host;NVPTX;AMDGPU\" \\\n"
"        -DLLVM_ENABLE_LLD=ON \\\n"
"        -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=${LLVM_INSTALL_PREFIX}\n"
"    ninja install\n"
"\n"
"    # 拷贝FILECHECK到目标安装路径\n"
"    cp  {PATH_TO}/llvm-project/build/bin/FileCheck ${LLVM_INSTALL_PREFIX}/bin/FileCheck\n"
"    ```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:48
msgid "3. **编译Triton-Asecnd**"
msgstr "3. **Compile Triton-Asecnd**"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:50
msgid ""
"    ```bash\n"
"    git clone https://github.com/triton-lang/triton-ascend.git && cd triton-ascend\n"
"    LLVM_SYSPATH=${LLVM_INSTALL_PREFIX} \\\n"
"    TRITON_BUILD_WITH_CCACHE=true \\\n"
"    TRITON_BUILD_WITH_CLANG_LLD=true \\\n"
"    TRITON_BUILD_PROTON=OFF \\\n"
"    TRITON_WHEEL_NAME=\"triton-ascend\" \\\n"
"    TRITON_APPEND_CMAKE_ARGS=\"-DTRITON_BUILD_UT=OFF\" \\\n"
"    python3 setup.py install\n"
"    ```\n"
msgstr ""

