#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:58
msgid "### 镜像使用"
msgstr "### Using Images"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:60
msgid ""
"```bash\n"
"docker run -u 0 -dit --shm-size=512g --name=triton-ascend_container \\\n"
"--security-opt seccomp=unconfined \\\n"
"--device=/dev/davinci0 \\\n"
"--device=/dev/davinci1 \\\n"
"--device=/dev/davinci2 \\\n"
"--device=/dev/davinci3 \\\n"
"--device=/dev/davinci4 \\\n"
"--device=/dev/davinci5 \\\n"
"--device=/dev/davinci6 \\\n"
"--device=/dev/davinci7 \\\n"
"--device=/dev/davinci_manager \\\n"
"--device=/dev/devmm_svm \\\n"
"--device=/dev/hisi_hdc \\\n"
"-v /usr/local/dcmi:/usr/local/dcmi \\\n"
"-v /usr/local/bin/npu-smi:/usr/local/bin/npu-smi \\\n"
"-v /usr/local/sbin/npu-smi:/usr/local/sbin/npu-smi \\\n"
"-v /usr/local/Ascend/driver:/usr/local/Ascend/driver \\\n"
"-v /home:/home \\\n"
"-v /etc/ascend_install.info:/etc/ascend_install.info \\\n"
"triton-ascend-image:latest \\\n"
"/bin/bash\n"
"\n"
"# 进入容器，可在前面的快速安装和源码安装中任选一种方式安装Triton-Ascend\n"
"docker exec -u root -it triton-ascend_container /bin/bash\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:62
msgid "## 运行样例"
msgstr "## Running Examples"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:64
msgid "**运行tutorials中向量加法实例验证结果**"
msgstr "**Run the vector addition example in tutorials to verify the result**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:66
msgid "向量加法实例：<a href=\"https://github.com/triton-lang/triton-ascend/blob/main/third_party/ascend/tutorials/01-vector-add.py\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: #0066cc;\">01-vector-add.py </a>"
msgstr "Vector Addition Example: <a href=\"https://github.com/triton-lang/triton-ascend/blob/main/third_party/ascend/tutorials/01-vector-add.py\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: #0066cc;\">01-vector-add.py </a>"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:68
msgid ""
"```bash\n"
"# 设置CANN环境变量（以root用户默认安装路径`/usr/local/Ascend`为例）\n"
"source /usr/local/Ascend/ascend-toolkit/set_env.sh\n"
"# 拉取triton-ascend源码仓及用例（可选，非源码编译安装运行示例时需拉源码仓）\n"
"git clone https://github.com/triton-lang/triton-ascend.git\n"
"# 运行tutorials实例\n"
"python3 ./third_party/ascend/tutorials/01-vector-add.py\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:70
msgid "观察到类似的输出即说明环境配置正确："
msgstr "Observing similar output indicates that the environment configuration is correct:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:72
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"tensor([0.8329, 1.0024, 1.3639,  ..., 1.0796, 1.0406, 1.5811], device='npu:0')\n"
"tensor([0.8329, 1.0024, 1.3639,  ..., 1.0796, 1.0406, 1.5811], device='npu:0')\n"
"The maximum difference between torch and triton is 0.0\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:74
msgid "## 安装常见问题"
msgstr "## Installation FAQ"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:76
msgid "**问题一：安装TorchNPU时出现报错“ERROR: No matching distribution found for torch==2.7.1+cpu”**"
msgstr "**Issue 1: Error \"ERROR: No matching distribution found for torch==2.7.1+cpu\" occurs when installing TorchNPU**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:80
msgid "可以尝试手动安装Torch后再安装TorchNPU："
msgstr "You can try manually installing Torch first, then install TorchNPU."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:82
msgid ""
"```bash\n"
"pip install torch==2.7.1+cpu --index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cpu\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:84
msgid "**问题二：编译安装Triton-Ascend时，如果GCC < 9.4.0，可能报错 “ld.lld: error: unable to find library -lstdc++fs”**"
msgstr "**Issue 2: When compiling and installing Triton-Ascend, if GCC < 9.4.0, the error \"ld.lld: error: unable to find library -lstdc++fs\" may occur.**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:88
msgid ""
"一般是链接器无法找到stdc++fs库引起的报错。该库用于支持GCC 9之前版本的文件系统特性。此时需要手动把CMake文件中以下相关代码片段的注释打开。\n"
"文件路径：triton-ascend/CMakeLists.txt\n"
msgstr ""
"This error is usually caused by the linker being unable to find the stdc++fs library. This library is used to support filesystem features in versions prior to GCC 9. In this case, you need to manually uncomment the relevant code snippet in the CMake file below.  \n"
"File path: triton-ascend/CMakeLists.txt\n"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:90
msgid ""
"```bash\n"
"if (NOT WIN32 AND NOT APPLE)\n"
"link_libraries(stdc++fs)\n"
"endif()\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:92
msgid "**问题三：执行算子时报错 ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'triton._C.libtriton.ascend'; 'triton._C.libtriton' is not a package**"
msgstr "**Issue 3: When executing an operator, an error is reported: ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'triton._C.libtriton.ascend'; 'triton._C.libtriton' is not a package**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:94
msgid "**根因分析**"
msgstr "**Root Cause Analysis**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:96
msgid " triton-ascend目录被triton覆盖,导致triton-ascend功能受损。"
msgstr "The triton-ascend directory is overwritten by triton, causing triton-ascend functionality to be impaired."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:98
msgid "**解决措施**"
msgstr "**Solution**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:100
msgid " 卸载已损坏的triton-ascend,重新安装即可。以3.2.1 版本为例，可执行如下命令修复："
msgstr "Uninstall the damaged triton-ascend, then reinstall it. Taking version 3.2.1 as an example, you can execute the following command to fix it:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:102
msgid ""
"```bash\n"
"pip uninstall triton-ascend triton\n"
"pip install triton-ascend==3.2.1 --extra-index-url=https://triton-ascend.osinfra.cn/pypi/simple\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:104
msgid "**问题四：Triton-Ascend 3.2.1版本为何新增依赖triton？**"
msgstr "**Question 4: Why does Triton-Ascend version 3.2.1 add a dependency on triton?**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:106
msgid ""
"答复：Triton-Ascend是基于Triton进行的二次开发，与Triton安装目录同名。若用户安装Triton-Ascend之后，在此安装Triton或依赖Triton的三方件，会覆盖Triton目录，导致Triton-Ascend功能受损。\n"
"因此通过增加Triton依赖，当Triton被覆盖安装时会有如下提醒。\n"
msgstr "Answer: Triton-Ascend is a secondary development based on Triton, and it shares the same installation directory name as Triton. If users install Triton or third-party components that depend on Triton after installing Triton-Ascend, the Triton directory will be overwritten, causing damage to Triton-Ascend's functionality. Therefore, by adding a Triton dependency, the following warning will be displayed when Triton is overwritten during installation."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:108
msgid ""
"```text\n"
"ERROR: pip's dependency resolver does not currently take into account all the packages that are installed. This behaviour is the source of the following dependency conflicts.\n"
"triton-ascend 3.2.1 requires triton==3.5.0, but you have triton 3.5.1 which is incompatible.\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:110
msgid "若用户遇到且想恢复Triton-Ascend功能，可做如下操作："
msgstr "If users encounter issues and wish to restore the Triton-Ascend functionality, they can perform the following operations:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:112
msgid ""
"```bash\n"
"pip uninstall triton-ascend triton\n"
"pip install triton-ascend==3.2.1 --extra-index-url=https://triton-ascend.osinfra.cn/pypi/simple\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:114
msgid "**问题五：Triton-Ascend 3.2.1版本依赖的Triton版本为何不一致？**"
msgstr "**Question 5: Why are the Triton versions that Triton-Ascend 3.2.1 depends on inconsistent?**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:116
msgid "答复：X86与Arm使用不同版本的社区Triton安装包，是因为社区从Triton 3.2版本开始提供X86安装包，而Arm安装包是从Triton 3.5版本开始提供的。"
msgstr "Answer: The community provides different versions of the Triton installation package for X86 and Arm because the community started offering the X86 installation package from Triton version 3.2, while the Arm installation package has been available since Triton version 3.5."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:118
msgid "**问题六：如何确认芯片类型**"
msgstr "**Question 6: How to Confirm the Chip Type**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:120
msgid "您可以使用npu-smi命令查看系统上的NPU型号。例如，在npu-smi info命令的输出中，\"910B4\" 对应芯片类型A2（昇腾910b系列）："
msgstr "You can use the `npu-smi` command to check the NPU model on the system. For example, in the output of the `npu-smi info` command, \"910B4\" corresponds to chip type A2 (Ascend 910B series)."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/installation_guide.md:122
msgid ""
"```Text\n"
"root@localhost:/# npu-smi  info\n"
"+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n"
"| npu-smi 26.0.rc1                            Version: 26.0.rc1                                                    |\n"
"+---------------------------+---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------+\n"
"| NPU   Name                | Health        | Power(W)             Temp(C)                 Hugepages-Usage(page)   |\n"
"| Chip                      | Bus-Id        | AICore(%)            Memory-Usage(MB)        HBM-Usage(MB)           |\n"
"+===========================+===============+======================================================================+\n"
"| 0     910B4               | OK            | 82.6                 32                      0    / 0                |\n"
"| 0                         | 0000:C1:00.0  | 0                    0    / 0                2871 / 32768            |\n"
"+===========================+===============+======================================================================+\n"
"+---------------------------+---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------+\n"
"| NPU     Chip              | Process id    | Process name       | Process memory(MB)    | Process id in container |\n"
"+===========================+===============+======================================================================+\n"
"| No running processes found in NPU 0                                                                              |\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

